      <item>
         <title>Version 0.1.1</title>
			    <description><![CDATA[
					<table style="border: dotted 1px #ccc;" width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
					   <tr>
					        <td style="background-color: #e6edff;margin: -3px" colspan="2">
					                <h3>Minor update (0.1.1)</h3>
					        </td>
					   </tr>
					   <tr>
					        <td valign="top">
					            <p>Some minor changes:
									<ul>
										<li>A smaller menu bar icon to save some space.</li>
										<li>Support for the new url field of the Prowl API. </li>
										<li>Support for new API base url.</li>
									</ul>
								</p>
					        </td>
