      <item>
            <title>Version 0.1 (initial release)</title>
			    <description><![CDATA[
					<table style="border: dotted 1px #ccc;" width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
					   <tr>
					        <td style="background-color: #e6edff;margin: -3px" colspan="2">
					                <h3>Initial release (0.1)</h3>
					        </td>
					   </tr>
					   <tr>
					        <td valign="top">
					            <p>Sends a text message from Mac OS to the Prowl app 
								on your iPhone. Currently supports:
									<ul>
										<li>Copy text from clipboard</li>
										<li>Send selected text via the services menu</li>
										<li>Send text via the Applescript interface</li>
									</ul>
								</p>
					        </td>
					   </tr>
					</table>
			    ]]></description>
			
